# --- Output Management ---
outputs/* # Ignore all subfolders in outputs
!outputs/reports/        # UN-IGNORE the reports folder
!outputs/reports/*.pdf   # Specifically allow your portfolios
!outputs/hunter/         # UN-IGNORE the hunter folder
outputs/hunter/cutouts/  # But STILL IGNORE the thousands of JPGs
outputs/hunter/plots/    # STILL IGNORE diagnostic plots
!outputs/hunter/*.csv    # KEEP the final candidate CSVs